display.description: Just tells the bot to copy your message using plain text or embed.

randomslap.description: Slaps a random member in a server.

8ball.description: An implementation of the 8ball fortune teller toy.

iseven.description: Checks if a number is even or not.

slap.description: Slaps a member in a server.

hack.description: Hacks a member in a server.

ban.description: Bans a member in a server.

kick.description: Kicks a member in a server.

unban.description: Unbans a member in a server.

banlist.description: Returns a list of banned members in a server.

mute.description: Mutes a member in a server.

unmute.description: Unmutes a member in a server.

set-join-role.description: Adds role to users who joins the server.

set-join-channel.description: Tells the bot to send welcome messages in a certain channel in the server.

welcome-dm-message.description: Tells the bot to dm a user who joins a server.

remove-join-role.description: Tells the bot to stop adding roles to users who joins the server.

remove-join-channel.description: Tells the bot to stop sending welcome messages.

remove-dm-message.description: Tells the bot to stop dming users who joins the server.

add-mute-role.description: Tells the bot to add a mute role.

rock-paper-scissors.description: Wanna play rock paper scissors with a bot then this is the command for you.

dice.description: A dice game for you and termino.
